def _get_value(case):
    has_handles = len([h for h in case.bodies if type(h) is Handle]) > 0
    has_containers = len([c for c in case.bodies if type(c) is Container]) > 0
    has_fixed_connections = len([fc for fc in case.connections if type(fc) is FixedConnection]) > 0
    has_prismatic_connections = len([pc for pc in case.connections if type(pc) is PrismaticConnection]) > 0
    return has_handles and has_containers and has_fixed_connections and has_prismatic_connections
